%section.py-16.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8.bg-gray-50
  .max-w-6xl.mx-auto
    .text-center.mb-12
      %h2.text-3xl.md:text-4xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4
        Zero Commission, 100% Retained Revenue: The Wheels on Rent Pledge
      %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.mx-auto.max-w-3xl
        This is our key differentiator and your biggest commercial advantage. We believe you deserve to keep every Dirham earned from your hard work. Our platform operates on a simple, transparent subscription model, completely eliminating the need for brokerage fees or hidden commissions.

    %h3.text-3xl.md:text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mt-4.mb-4
      The Commission-Free Value Chain
    %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.mb-4
      Unlike aggregators that dilute your profits, our process ensures that the transaction remains entirely between you and the customer:

    - cache ['vendor_requests', 'commission_flow'] do
      .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-3.gap-8.mb-16
        / Card 1
        .bg-white.p-8.rounded-xl.shadow-md
          .w-12.h-12.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mb-4{style: "background-color: #3A6363"}
            %span.text-lg.font-bold.text-white 1
          %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
            Customer Inquiry
          %p.text-gray-600
            Renters contact us directly via phone, WhatsApp, or email.

        / Card 2
        .bg-white.p-8.rounded-xl.shadow-md
          .w-12.h-12.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mb-4{style: "background-color: #00B4D8"}
            %span.text-lg.font-bold.text-white 2
          %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
            Booking & Payment
          %p.text-gray-600
            You handle all invoicing and payment processing.

        / Card 3
        .bg-white.p-8.rounded-xl.shadow-md
          .w-12.h-12.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mb-4{style: "background-color: #3A6363"}
            %span.text-lg.font-bold.text-white 3
          %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-3
            Revenue Retention
          %p.text-gray-600
            You keep 100% of the rental earnings.

      / ========== COMPARISON TABLE SECTION ==========
      .overflow-x-auto.mb-16.-mx-4.px-4.sm:mx-0.sm:px-0
        %table.w-full.rounded-xl.border-2{style: "border-color: #3A6363; min-width: 640px"}
          %thead
            %tr.text-white{style: "background-color: #3A6363"}
              %th.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-left.font-bold.text-sm.sm:text-base Feature
              %th.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-left.font-bold.text-sm.sm:text-base Wheels on Rent Model (Subscription)
              %th.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-left.font-bold.text-sm.sm:text-base Traditional Broker Model (Commission)

          %tbody
            / Row 1
            %tr.border-b.border-gray-200.hover:bg-gray-50
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.font-semibold.text-gray-900.text-sm.sm:text-base Revenue Share
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700
                .flex.items-start
                  %svg.w-4.sm:w-5.h-4.sm:h-5.mr-2.flex-shrink-0.mt-0.5{fill: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', style: 'color: #00B4D8'}
                    %path{d: 'M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z'}
                  %span.text-gray-600.text-sm.sm:text-base You keep 100% of the rent
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700.text-sm.sm:text-base Brokers typically take 15% - 30%

            / Row 2
            %tr.border-b.border-gray-200.hover:bg-gray-50
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.font-semibold.text-gray-900.text-sm.sm:text-base Pricing Control
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700
                .flex.items-start
                  %svg.w-4.sm:w-5.h-4.sm:h-5.mr-2.flex-shrink-0.mt-0.5{fill: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', style: 'color: #00B4D8'}
                    %path{d: 'M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z'}
                  %span.text-gray-600.text-sm.sm:text-base Complete control; set and update rates instantly
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700.text-sm.sm:text-base Often pressured to lower rates to compete with broker offers

            / Row 3
            %tr.border-b.border-gray-200.hover:bg-gray-50
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.font-semibold.text-gray-900.text-sm.sm:text-base Customer Data
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700
                .flex.items-start
                  %svg.w-4.sm:w-5.h-4.sm:h-5.mr-2.flex-shrink-0.mt-0.5{fill: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', style: 'color: #00B4D8'}
                    %path{d: 'M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z'}
                  %span.text-gray-600.text-sm.sm:text-base You own the client relationship and contact data
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700.text-sm.sm:text-base Client data is controlled and owned by the third-party broker

            / Row 4
            %tr.hover:bg-gray-50
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.font-semibold.text-gray-900.text-sm.sm:text-base Cost Structure
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700
                .flex.items-start
                  %svg.w-4.sm:w-5.h-4.sm:h-5.mr-2.flex-shrink-0.mt-0.5{fill: 'currentColor', viewBox: '0 0 24 24', style: 'color: #00B4D8'}
                    %path{d: 'M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z'}
                  %span.text-gray-600.text-sm.sm:text-base Predictable, fixed monthly cost
              %td.px-3.sm:px-6.py-3.sm:py-4.text-gray-700.text-sm.sm:text-base Unpredictable, variable cost that scales with revenue

